tar, bailar y vibrar de emoción? Jarabe de palo, Radio futura, Alaska, Mecano, Miguel Rios, Los Secretos, Hombres G, Coti, etc? son solo algunos de los grupos o solistas que sonarán en este show.\\n¡Cántalo todo, siéntelo todo! ¡Viva el Pop Español!\",\"url\":\"https://www.universe.com/events/viva-el-pop-espanol-tickets-B3YVTH?ref=ticketmaster\",\"locale\":\"en-us\",\"images\":[{\"ratio\":\"4_3\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/60031903-c3dd-4504-8abe-5c28cfb9df9c/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/305x225/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":305,\"height\":225,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/60031903-c3dd-4504-8abe-5c28cfb9df9c/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/1024x576/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":576,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/f51/ee785ed6-f806-4195-98f4-69f67e09df51_106201_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_LARGE_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":2048,\"height\":1152,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/f51/ee785ed6-f806-4195-98f4-69f67e09df51_106201_RECOMENDATION_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":100,\"height\":56,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"3_2\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/60031903-c3dd-4504-8abe-5c28cfb9df9c/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/305x203/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":305,\"height\":203,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"3_2\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/60031903-c3dd-4504-8abe-5c28cfb9df9c/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/1024x683/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":683,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/f51/ee785ed6-f806-4195-98f4-69f67e09df51_106201_RETINA_PORTRAIT_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":640,\"height\":360,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/f51/ee785ed6-f806-4195-98f4-69f67e09df51_106201_EVENT_DETAIL_PAGE_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":205,\"height\":115,\"fallback\":true},{\