},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/797/5e693c26-2881-4776-8f0c-3aa94bfa3797_106511_RETINA_LANDSCAPE_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":1136,\"height\":639,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/797/5e693c26-2881-4776-8f0c-3aa94bfa3797_106511_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":576,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"3_2\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/797/5e693c26-2881-4776-8f0c-3aa94bfa3797_106511_RETINA_PORTRAIT_3_2.jpg\",\"width\":640,\"height\":427,\"fallback\":true}],\"classifications\":[{\"primary\":true,\"segment\":{\"id\":\"KZFzniwnSyZfZ7v7nJ\",\"name\":\"Music\"},\"genre\":{\"id\":\"KnvZfZ7vAvv\",\"name\":\"Alternative\"},\"subGenre\":{\"id\":\"KZazBEonSMnZfZ7vAde\",\"name\":\"Indie Rock\"},\"type\":{\"id\":\"KZAyXgnZfZ7v7l1\",\"name\":\"Group\"},\"subType\":{\"id\":\"KZFzBErXgnZfZ7vA71\",\"name\":\"Band\"},\"family\":false}],\"upcomingEvents\":{\"universe\":2,\"_total\":2,\"_filtered\":0},\"_links\":{\"self\":{\"href\":\"/discovery/v2/attractions/K8vZ917rnQ0?locale=en-us\"}}}]}},{\"name\":\"Puzzle, el show que te hará cuestionarte la realidad\",\"type\":\"event\",\"id\":\"LvZ18Qb9uFEFDWZZvWW6H\",\"test\":false,\"description\":\" \\nEn Puzzle, experimentarás una combinación única de habilidades como la psicología, comunicación no verbal, y comedia, en una hora llena de fenómenos extraordinarios: desde la precognición y coincidencias imposibles hasta el icónico \'oráculo\', donde Fito Crawford desvela los secretos del futuro de los asistentes.\\nTodo ello aderezado con el humor agudo y elegante de Fito Crawford. Un show con múltiples elementos que encajan a la perfección, formando un todo donde la pieza final está dentro de tu propia mente.\\n¿Estás listo para descubrir dónde encajas? No te pierdas Puzzle, el show que te hará cuestionarte la realidad en ESPACIO HOLLYWOOD.\",\"url\":\"https://www.universe.com/events/puzzle-el-show-que-te-hara-cuestionarte-la-realidad-tickets-RQ4MSD?ref=ticketmaster\",\"locale\":\"en-us\",\"images\":[{\"ratio\":\"3_2\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/cab78b69-8031-4cbd-88b1-d3ec12eef67b/-/resize/1200x/-/crop/1200x1200/0,0/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/305x203/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":305,\"height\":203,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/f51/ee785ed6-f806-4195-98f4-69f67e09df51_106201_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_LARGE_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":2048,\"height\":1152,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"3_2\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/cab78b69-8031-4cbd-88b1-d3ec12eef67b/-/resize/1200x/-/crop/1200x1200/0,0/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/1024x683/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":683,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/f51/ee785ed6-f806-4195-98f4-69f67e09df51_106201_RECOMENDATION_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":100,\"height\":56,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"3_2\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/cab78b69-8031-4cbd-88b1-d3ec12eef67b/-/resize/1200x/-/crop/1200x1200/0,0/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/640x427/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":640,\"height\":427,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/cab78b69-8031-4cbd-88b1-d3ec12eef67b/-/resize/1200x/-/crop/1200x1200/0,0/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/1024x576/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":576,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/f51/ee785ed6-f806-4195-98f4-69f67e09df51_106201_RETINA_PORTRAIT_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":640,\"height\":360,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/f51/ee785ed6-f806-4195-98f4-69f67e09df51_106201_EVENT_DETAIL_PAGE_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":205,\"height\":115,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"4_3\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/cab78b69-8031-4cbd-88b1-d3ec12eef67b/-/resize/1200x/-/crop/1200x1200/0,0/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/305x225/center/-/progressive/yes/-