cador o revolucionario? Pasea por este increíble espacio inmersivo, y acércate como nunca antes al escurridizo artista británico y a las incógnitas que le rodean. ¡Consigue tus entradas para el Museo Banksy en Madrid!Black Friday \",\"url\":\"https://www.universe.com/events/museo-banksy-madrid-tickets-X38GZF?ref=ticketmaster\",\"locale\":\"en-us\",\"images\":[{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/71a/8ec88564-616d-465d-979a-53eae342571a_106151_EVENT_DETAIL_PAGE_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":205,\"height\":115,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"4_3\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/f899bfae-9c90-4178-93c8-20c27886199a/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/305x225/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":305,\"height\":225,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"3_2\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/f899bfae-9c90-4178-93c8-20c27886199a/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/1024x683/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":683,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/f899bfae-9c90-4178-93c8-20c27886199a/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/1024x576/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":576,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"3_2\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/f899bfae-9c90-4178-93c8-20c27886199a/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/305x203/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":305,\"height\":203,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/71a/8ec88564-616d-465d-979a-53eae342571a_106151_RETINA_LANDSCAPE_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":1136,\"height\":639,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/71a/8ec88564-616d-465d-979a-53eae342571a_106151_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_LARGE_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":2048,\"height\":1152,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/71a/8ec88564-616d-465d-979a-53eae342571a_106151_RETINA_PORTRAIT_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":640,\"height\":360,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"3_2