 Pennesi, Facundo Quirós\\nCoreografías: Facundo Quirós\\nProducción: Inspira, La Opción\\nArtistas: Álvaro Prieto Expósito, Daniel Fernández, Nicole Da Diva, Facundo Pennesi, Facundo Quirós, Marina Ranuschio, Soledad Barderas, Victoria Condomi.\\nTécnica: Miguel Ocaña\\n\",\"url\":\"https://www.universe.com/events/vespera-cabaret-erotico-tickets-4T72ND?ref=ticketmaster\",\"locale\":\"en-us\",\"images\":[{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/f51/ee785ed6-f806-4195-98f4-69f67e09df51_106201_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_LARGE_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":2048,\"height\":1152,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"4_3\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/9bcc9627-b9bb-409e-81d6-d3f72ee1cd49/-/resize/1200x/-/crop/1200x1200/0,0/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/305x225/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":305,\"height\":225,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"3_2\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/9bcc9627-b9bb-409e-81d6-d3f72ee1cd49/-/resize/1200x/-/crop/1200x1200/0,0/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/305x203/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":305,\"height\":203,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/f51/ee785ed6-f806-4195-98f4-69f67e09df51_106201_RECOMENDATION_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":100,\"height\":56,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/f51/ee785ed6-f806-4195-98f4-69f67e09df51_106201_RETINA_PORTRAIT_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":640,\"height\":360,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/9bcc9627-b9bb-409e-81d6-d3f72ee1cd49/-/resize/1200x/-/crop/1200x1200/0,0/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/1024x576/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":576,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"3_2\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/9bcc9627-b9bb-409e-81d6-d3f72ee1cd49/-/resize/1200x/-/crop/1200x1200/0,0/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/640x427/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":640,\"height\":427,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"16_9