ios para que el género del bolero y la balada lleguen desde principio a fin del concierto a todos los públicos.\\nDéjate llevar por la música de Luis Miguel, el artista que dominó el bolero y la balada y nos hizo vibrar desde México hasta España.\",\"url\":\"https://www.universe.com/events/tributo-a-luis-miguel-el-sol-de-mexico-tickets-P0VG4T?ref=ticketmaster\",\"locale\":\"en-us\",\"images\":[{\"ratio\":\"3_2\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/c212e587-50b7-4e74-bfc4-702b08bc153a/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/1024x683/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":683,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/f51/ee785ed6-f806-4195-98f4-69f67e09df51_106201_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_LARGE_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":2048,\"height\":1152,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"3_2\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/c212e587-50b7-4e74-bfc4-702b08bc153a/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/305x203/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":305,\"height\":203,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/c212e587-50b7-4e74-bfc4-702b08bc153a/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/1024x576/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":576,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/f51/ee785ed6-f806-4195-98f4-69f67e09df51_106201_RECOMENDATION_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":100,\"height\":56,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/f51/ee785ed6-f806-4195-98f4-69f67e09df51_106201_RETINA_PORTRAIT_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":640,\"height\":360,\"fallback\":true},{\"ratio\":\"4_3\",\"url\":\"https://images.universe.com/c212e587-50b7-4e74-bfc4-702b08bc153a/-/format/jpeg/-/scale_crop/305x225/center/-/progressive/yes/-/inline/yes/\",\"width\":305,\"height\":225,\"fallback\":false},{\"ratio\":\"16_9\",\"url\":\"https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/c/f51/ee785ed6-f806-4195-98f4-69f67e09df51_106201_EVENT_DETAIL_PAGE_16_9.jpg\",\"width\":205,\"height\":115,\"fal